headline: Insights Into Targa Resources (TRGP) Q4: Wall Street Projections for Key Metrics
summary: Beyond analysts' top-and-bottom-line estimates for Targa Resources (TRGP), evaluate projections for some of its key metrics to gain a better insight into how the business might have performed for the quarter ended December 2025.
